{
  "id": "campaign_guides/legacy_of_the_ancestors/81_oura_vos_traveler_loa/81_4_loa",
  "lookup_group": "campaign_guides/legacy_of_the_ancestors",
  "lookup_id": "81.4",
  "title": "81.4 (LOA)",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Dace places a comforting hand on Oura\u2019s shoulder. \u201cYou\u2019ve nothing to fear,\u201d she says. \u201cIf you fall, I will summon a cushion of air to carry you gently to the ground.\u201d"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\u201cAre you sure it will work?\u201d asks Oura. \u201cYou\u2019ve done this before, right?\u201d"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\u201cOf course!\u201d says Dace, displaying the same brand of confidence you\u2019ve witnessed in her brother. \u201cI\u2019ve carried myself on the wind dozens of times. Hundreds! Theoretically, carrying someone else should be more or less the same. It\u2019s perfectly safe.\u201d"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Oura\u2019s eyes widen for a moment. Then, with a look of determination on her face, Oura nods, turns, and begins her ascent."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As you watch her climb, you feel a sudden stir of emotion."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h4",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Rangers Choose"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [],
          "link": {
            "id": null,
            "anchor": "rangers-choose",
            "url": "#rangers-choose"
          }
        }
      ],
      "anchor": "rangers-choose"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "span",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "A) You feel inspired to join her."
                }
              ],
              "color": "red"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Without giving it a second thought, you remove your pack and follow Oura\u2019s example. After hours of climbing, you reach the summit shortly after she does. Dace didn\u2019t need to so much as lift a finger. Exhausted but invigorated, you gaze upon the Valley. \u201cI can\u2019t wait to tell Quisi,\u201d says Oura."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Each Ranger discards all their"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "FIT"
            }
          ],
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "energy and soothes all fatigue. Record"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "MADE THE CLIMB"
            }
          ],
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "on the campaign tracker."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "span",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "B) You feel relieved to be on solid ground."
                }
              ],
              "color": "red"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You watch Oura climb. It takes her many hours to reach the summit. When she does, you hear her whoop in celebration. \u201cReady to come down?\u201d Dace shouts. In answer, Oura leaps from the cliff. After the longest moment of your life, Dace gestures toward her with her conduit. You feel the wind whip around you, then you watch in amazement as Oura floats gently to the ground."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\u201cYou see?\u201d Dace says with a grin. \u201cPerfectly safe.\u201d"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Record"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "STAYED PUT"
            }
          ],
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "on the campaign tracker."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\u00bb Continue reading:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Gain the Carried By the Wind reward card. Discard Dace and Oura. Return"
        },
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "HELPING HAND"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "to the collection."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
